	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are several reasons: 
<br /><ul><li>The FDS BIOS is copyrighted until after you are dead. It would have to be rewritten anyway to access a disk image in bankswitched RAM. </li><li>PowerPak has a 72-pin connector. The 72-pin connector has no audio pins. </li></ul>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


